y needs to be included in the build</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Build Process</h2>\n<p>The build process:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Reads all markdown files from <code>content/notes/</code></li>\n<li>Generates static pages for each note</li>\n<li>Pre-renders the home page with the notes list</li>\n<li>API routes are serverless functions</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>CORS for Production</h2>\n<p>The API endpoints have CORS headers set to <code>*</code> to allow any client to consume them. This is important for the decentralized dev notes community.</p>\n<h2>Next Steps After Deployment</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Update metadata.json with production URL</li>\n<li>Test all three endpoints</li>\n<li>Share the metadata URL in the event chat</li>\n<li>Start working on the aggregator client (Paso 2)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The metadata endpoint will be at: <code>https://[your-domain].vercel.app/api/metadata.json</code></p>\n</div></main><footer class=\"footer\"><p>Built with Next.js • Deployed on Vercel</p></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-c8441f2d519541e3.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/d753f4838feb0173.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2:I[2846,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[4707,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n7:I[6423,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n9:I[1060,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:[\\\"slug\\\",\\\"2024-01-19-vercel-deployment\\\",\\\"d\\\"]\\na:[]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2\\\",null,{\\\"buildId\\\":\\\"_uB49DAU_UWYsY4PWCQH2\\\",\\\"assetPrefix\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlParts\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"notes\\\",\\\"2024-01-19-vercel-deployment\\\"],\\\"initialTree\\\":[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"notes\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"slug\\\",\\\"2024-01-19-vercel-deployment\\\",\\\"d\\\"],{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__?{\\\\\\\"slug\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2024-01-19-vercel-deployment\\\\\\\"}\\\",{}]}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],\\\"i